-- @reg name=ctrl
-- @field bits=0 name=enable access=RW

-- expected: error
-- error type: LoweringError
-- error message: "Require an offset key."
-- error location: line 1 (the `@reg` annotation)
-- reason: every `@reg` must carry an `offset=` key — the offset is what
--         distinguishes registers within a peripheral and feeds directly into
--         generated read/write accessors. Without it, codegen has nothing to
--         emit.
